│ A simple fix is to check if the current element's data range overlaps with the requested read range (`Offset` to `Offset +   │
│ BytesToRead`). If there is no overlap, we should skip processing that element entirely.                                      │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ In `ReadDataFromGlobal`, before processing an element `C` at `ElemOffset`, I will add a check:                               │
